From 5a555215faaee290c0e64b582bea6c08180050be Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Sowmiya Sree Elavalagan <ssreeela@qti.qualcomm.com>
Date: Thu, 26 Jun 2025 12:52:00 +0530
Subject: [PATCH] UPSTREAM:PROTOCOL:DP:wifi:ath12k:Add connectivity debug

Added two new ath12k debug mask, ATH12K_DBG_MLME and ATH12K_DBG_EAPOL.
This is to track various stages of association. Authentication,
association and disconnection flows comes under ATH12K_DBG_MLME mask.
EAPOL handshakes, key installation and removal comes under
ATH12K_DBG_EAPOL mask.

In addition to it EAPOL frame parser is added in data path to
differentiate between various EAPOL messages.

Debug mask level is moved to another module param to untilize the
remaining bits to accommodate additional mask.

Usage:
echo 3 > /sys/module/ath12k/parameters/debug_level
All the debug of level 3 and below would be enabled.

Patch-dependency: none

Signed-off-by: Sowmiya Sree Elavalagan <ssreeela@qti.qualcomm.com>
Signed-off-by: Yuvasree Sivasankaran <ysivasan@qti.qualcomm.com>
